{"tid":1362079,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【不合作】罷搭港鐵日/提早宣傳變相令市民改搭交通工具","createTime":"2019-07-24T18:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T11:01:46.000Z","uid":151571,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b05aa11e5574b6ce68e40833503ef1703422c9e2","tid":1362079,"uid":151571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:35:28.000Z","msg":"不合作運動 能夠引起的回響不少，亦係我地訴求、發聲既一種方法。但己所不欲勿施於人，應給予選擇性被塞車既權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA 罷搭港鐵日<br />\n以港鐵助長元朗黑夜、金鐘無故不停站等事件，連同光復、遊行等運動集體號召港人<span style=\"color: orange;\">每月/逢日</span>罷搭港鐵。<br />\n<br />\n或<br />\n<br />\nB 提早宣傳，相對令較多市民提早知悉。<br />\n當日在站外 人手或資料形式 提供附近交通路線，令受眾減低<br />\n<br />\ngood：<br />\n+減少市民不方便，無需突發轉乘交通/<span style=\"color: pink;\">被動</span>塞在港鐵內<br />\n+市民參與，增加認受性，正面輿論增加，給予港鐵壓力上升，集中民怨轉回槍頭<br />\n減少逢日因遊行既收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbad:<br />\n戰線增加，人員被分散<br />\n文宣工作增加<br />\n提早宣傳/站外宣傳，又多左個位比人搞事<br />\n<br />\n小弟愚笨，想法及文字粗略，各位見諒。<br />\n<br />\n可行性有嗎？各位巴絲隨意加減批評。"},{"pid":"94b05ad4c79172602ff85c5447596bd47dd2b3d2","tid":1362079,"uid":151571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea39c360d418e4435a10b71954aad78a9d6459b","tid":1362079,"uid":157453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:05:28.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總好過齋批評話搞著市民<br />\n<br />\n亦支持集體衝閘"},{"pid":"e8ea66a8b144bae4624bf76bf16f92b54ad9e668","tid":1362079,"uid":157453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces